  "items": [
    {
      "text": "案例一：火山引擎 WebSocket 风格 — 用 stylePrompt 自然语言控制情绪和声线。旁白开场，声音明亮圆润，带一点娓娓道来的感觉。",
      "role": "narrator",
      "stylePrompt": "女声，青年音色，音调中等，音色明亮圆润，声音厚度适中；发音清晰自然，气息平稳；情绪平静略带温暖，娓娓道来；语速0.95，句尾自然收束。"
    },
    {
      "text": "我没有背叛你。",
      "role": "male_lead",
      "stylePrompt": "男声，青年音色，音调中等，音色明亮圆润；发音清晰，气息由稳转急；情绪压抑克制，带一丝委屈；语速0.95，句末短停120ms，句尾压低。"
    },
    {
      "text": "那你为什么一直不解释？",
      "role": "female_lead",
      "stylePrompt": "女声，青年音色，音调中等偏高，清亮柔和但带质问感；发音清晰，气息略急；情绪焦急带责备；语速0.92，重读'为什么'，句尾压低。"
    },
    {
      "text": "案例二：MiniMax HTTP 风格 — 用 options.voiceSetting.emotion 枚举值控制情绪。",
      "role": "narrator",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "calm", "speed": 0.95 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "老公，人家要抱抱",
      "role": "female_lead",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "happy", "speed": 0.92 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "好好好",
      "role": "male_lead",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "calm", "speed": 1.0 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "案例三：MiniMax 停顿标记 — 用 <#秒数#> 控制对话节奏，比如 <#0.5#> 就是停顿半秒。",
      "role": "narrator",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "calm", "speed": 0.94 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "老公~<#0.08#>人家要抱抱",
      "role": "female_lead",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "happy", "speed": 0.92 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "好<#0.1#>好<#0.1#>好",
      "role": "male_lead",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "calm", "speed": 1.0 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "案例四：MiniMax 语气词标签 — 用 (laughs)、(sighs)、(breath) 等标签添加自然的语气。",
      "role": "narrator",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "calm", "speed": 0.94 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "好<#0.1#>好<#0.1#>好(laughs)",
      "role": "male_lead",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "calm", "speed": 1.0 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "案例五：MiniMax 多情绪切换 — calm、sad、happy、surprised、fearful、angry 全部来一遍。",
      "role": "narrator",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "calm", "speed": 0.94 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "你有没有想过，人一定要热爱些什么，才不至于被这无趣的生活吞没。",
      "role": "female_lead",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "calm", "speed": 0.95 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "可是我们每天奔波忙碌，不就是为了活下去吗？",
      "role": "female_lead",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "sad", "speed": 0.96 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "那精神需要什么？",
      "role": "female_lead",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "surprised", "speed": 0.97 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "它需要的是山川河流、自由，和那些真正能让心活过来的东西。",
      "role": "female_lead",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "happy", "speed": 0.93 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "哪怕生活一直颠簸，也还是可以吗？",
      "role": "female_lead",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "fearful", "speed": 0.97 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "当然可以。在颠簸的生活里，也要闪亮地过。",
      "role": "female_lead",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "happy", "speed": 0.92 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "案例六：voiceType 直指定 — 不通过 roleMap，直接用 MiniMax 的音色 ID 来指定声音。",
      "role": "narrator",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "calm", "speed": 0.94 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "哥哥，今晚先抱我一下好不好？<#0.2#>我都在门口等你好久了。",
      "voiceType": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Sweet_Lady",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "happy", "speed": 0.93 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "你倒是会抢先。<#0.2#>他刚回来，当然应该先来我这边坐。",
      "voiceType": "Arrogant_Miss",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "disgusted", "speed": 0.96 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "我鞋都还没换，你们两个就一人拉我一只手。",
      "voiceType": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "surprised", "speed": 0.92 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "案例七：MiniMax 音效控制 — voiceModify.soundEffects 添加礼堂回音、电话失真等音效。",
      "role": "narrator",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "calm", "speed": 0.94 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "各位旅客请注意，列车即将到站，请带好随身物品。",
      "role": "narrator",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "calm", "speed": 0.9 },
        "voiceModify": { "soundEffects": "auditorium_echo" }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "喂？听得到吗？信号好像不太好。",
      "role": "male_lead",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "surprised" },
        "voiceModify": { "soundEffects": "lofi_telephone" }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "案例八：MiniMax 音色微调 — voiceModify 的 pitch、timbre、intensity 参数调整声音质感。",
      "role": "narrator",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "calm", "speed": 0.94 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "在这个世界上，有些声音天生就带着力量感。",
      "role": "male_lead",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "calm", "speed": 0.95 },
        "voiceModify": { "pitch": -20, "intensity": -15, "timbre": -10 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "案例九：Edge TTS 风格 — 通过 options.style、speed、pitch 控制语音风格。",
      "role": "narrator",
      "provider": "edge_tts",
      "options": { "style": "newscast", "speed": 1.05, "pitch": "0" }
    },
    {
      "text": "今天的天气不错，气温在二十五度左右，适合出行。",
      "role": "narrator",
      "provider": "edge_tts",
      "options": { "style": "newscast", "speed": 1.05, "pitch": "0" }
    },
    {
      "text": "别担心，我会陪着你。",
      "role": "female_lead",
      "provider": "edge_tts",
      "options": { "style": "calm", "speed": 0.95, "pitch": "-10" }
    },
    {
      "text": "我们现在出发。",
      "role": "male_lead",
      "provider": "edge_tts",
      "options": { "style": "cheerful", "speed": 1.0, "pitch": "5" }
    },
    {
      "text": "案例十：多人对话 + 复杂情绪交织 — 甜妹撒娇、傲娇吃醋、绅士无奈，情绪快速切换，停顿+语气词全上。",
      "role": "narrator",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "calm", "speed": 0.94 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "哥哥~今天加班好晚，我好想你呀<#0.3#>先抱一下嘛(laughs)",
      "voiceType": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Sweet_Lady",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "happy", "speed": 0.93 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "她每次都说就一下。<#0.2#>结果最后整个人都黏在你怀里。",
      "voiceType": "Arrogant_Miss",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "angry", "speed": 0.97 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "我黏他怎么了？他身上暖暖的，抱起来本来就很舒服。",
      "voiceType": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Sweet_Lady",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "happy", "speed": 0.92 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "舒服也轮不到你先说。<#0.15#>今晚他要抱，也是先抱我。",
      "voiceType": "Arrogant_Miss",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "calm", "speed": 0.95 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "你们两个能不能别把'抱我'说得像在下命令。",
      "voiceType": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "calm", "speed": 0.91 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "那你喂我吃一口蛋糕好不好<#0.2#>就一小口(sighs)",
      "voiceType": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Sweet_Lady",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "happy", "speed": 0.92 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "我先走了。<#0.3#>你们两个，慢慢吵。",
      "voiceType": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "angry", "speed": 0.94 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "你敢。<#0.2#>我为了等你，连灯都没关。",
      "voiceType": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Sweet_Lady",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "sad", "speed": 0.96 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "我也没打算让你一个人走。<#0.15#>但如果必须选，那个人不会是她。",
      "voiceType": "Arrogant_Miss",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "disgusted", "speed": 1.0 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "够了。<#0.25#>再吵下去，今晚谁都别想好过。",
      "voiceType": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "angry", "speed": 0.94 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "案例十一：混合模式 — 同一个 JSON 里，部分条目用 stylePrompt（火山引擎），部分用 options（MiniMax），部分指定 provider 为 edge_tts。全局 provider 设为 auto，让系统自动判断。",
      "role": "narrator",
      "options": {
        "voiceSetting": { "emotion": "calm", "speed": 0.94 }
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "我没有背叛你。",
      "role": "male_lead",
      "stylePrompt": "男声，青年音色，音调中等，音色明亮圆润；情绪压抑克制；语速0.95，句尾短停120ms。"
    },
    {
      "text": "那你为什么<#0.3#>一直不解释？",
